<div class="wrapper top">
  <div class="py-96">
    <h1 class="text-center font-light font-body text-green-500 text-6xl mb-10 bg-yellow-200">
      かぎ針で何かを作るとき、<br>デザインや色の配色に迷いませんか？
    </h1>
    <h2 class="text-center font-body text-green-500 text-2xl mb-20 bg-yellow-200">アイデアを手助けすることにより、作る時に一層ワクワク感を引き出すサービスです。</h2>
  </div>
</div>
<section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
  <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
    <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font text-center text-gray-900 mb-20 font-body">About</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap sm:-m-4 -mx-4 -mb-10 -mt-4 md:space-y-0 space-y-6">
      <div class="p-4 md:w-1/3 flex">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-500 mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-grow pl-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium mb-2 font-body">Story</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-base font-body">私はかぎ針で編み物をしています。<br>その時に「作り終わった時に毛糸の配色がぱっとしなかった。」、「デザイン見て作り始めたい」と思うようになりこのサイトを作るきっかけになりました。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 md:w-1/3 flex border-l-2 border-gray-200">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-500 mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-grow pl-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium mb-2 font-body">What you can do</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-base font-body">
            好きな色を選択して完成したイメージを想像できたり、<br>イメージ別に配色をみれたりできます。<br>編み物する前に悩む配色も楽しみながら作っていきましょう🌼<br>※ログインすると塗った編み図を保存できて、比較することもできます。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 md:w-1/3 flex border-l-2 border-gray-200">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-500 mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v13m0-13V6a2 2 0 112 2h-2zm0 0V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 109.5 8H12zm-7 4h14M5 12a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 12v7a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-7" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-grow pl-6">
          <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium mb-2 font-body">Post your work</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-base font-body">かぎ針で作ったものを投稿することや<br>後で見ることもできます。<br>みなさんのアイデアのお手伝いを<br>投稿を通じてしませんか？</p>
            <div class="wrap flex justify-center ">
              <button class="mr-3 mt-3 text-green-500 inline-flex items-center font-body">
                <%= link_to ("/posts") do %>
                  投稿一覧へ
                <% end %>
              </button>
              <p class="font-body mt-3 text-green-500 mr-3">or</p>
              <button class="mt-3 text-green-500 inline-flex items-center font-body">
                <%= link_to ("/posts/new") do %>
                  投稿する！
                <% end %>
              </button>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="text-gray-600 body-font overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
    <div class="lg:w-4/5 mx-auto flex flex-wrap">
      <%= image_tag "Knitting.png", width: "500",heght: "500",class: "lg:w-1/2 w-full lg:h-auto h-64 object-cover object-center rounded"%>
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full lg:pl-10 lg:py-6 mt-6 lg:mt-40">
        <h1 class="text-gray-900 text-3xl title-font font-medium mb-1 font-body">Drawing Knitting diagrams</h1>
        <p class="leading-relaxed font-body lg:mt-10">
          持っている毛糸で色の組み合わせに迷っていませんか？<br>編み図に似せて色を塗って想像できるようにしました🌼
        </p>
        <button class=" bg-pink-300 hover:bg-pink-500 text-white font-body font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded w-2/6 h-16 justify-center items-center lg:mt-10">
          <%= link_to ("/draw") do %>
            色を塗ってみる
          <% end %>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class= "px-5">
  <h3 class="text-center text-pink-500 text-4xl mb-20 font-body ">イメージはあるけど配色が思いつかない...<br>イメージ別に配色を組み合わせました🌷<br></h3>

  <div class="mx-32 mt-7 w-5/6" id="tabs-id">
    <div class="w-full">
      <ul class="flex mb-0 list-none flex-wrap pt-3 pb-4 flex-row">
        <li class="-mb-px mr-2 last:mr-0 flex-auto text-center">
          <a class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-5 py-3 shadow-lg rounded block leading-normal text-white bg-pink-600 font-body" onclick="changeAtiveTab(event,'tab-cools')">
            かっこいい
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="-mb-px mr-2 last:mr-0 flex-auto text-center">
          <a class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-5 py-3 shadow-lg rounded block leading-normal text-pink-600 bg-white font-body" onclick="changeAtiveTab(event,'tab-retros')">
            レトロ
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="-mb-px mr-2 last:mr-0 flex-auto text-center">
          <a class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-5 py-3 shadow-lg rounded block leading-normal text-pink-600 bg-white font-body" onclick="changeAtiveTab(event,'tab-cuties')">
            かわいい
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="-mb-px mr-2 last:mr-0 flex-auto text-center">
          <a class="text-xs font-bold uppercase px-5 py-3 shadow-lg rounded block leading-normal text-pink-600 bg-white font-body" onclick="changeAtiveTab(event,'tab-unities')">
            統一感
          </a>
        </li>

      </ul>
      <div class=" flex flex-col min-w-0 break-words bg-white w-full mb-6 shadow-lg rounded">
        <div class="px-4 py-5 flex-auto">
          <div class="tab-content tab-space">
            <div class="block" id="tab-cools">
              <div class="swiper">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "かっこいい1.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "かっこいい2.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "かっこいい3.png" %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hidden" id="tab-retros">
              <div class="swiper">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "レトロ1.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "レトロ2.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "レトロ3.png" %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
              </div>

            </div>
            <div class="hidden" id="tab-cuties">
              <div class="swiper">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "かわいい1.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "かわいい2.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "かわいい3.png" %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden" id="tab-unities">
              <div class="swiper">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "統一感1.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "統一感2.png" %></div>
                  <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag "統一感3.png" %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script>
    function changeAtiveTab(event,tabID){
      let element = event.target;
      while(element.nodeName !== "A"){
        element = element.parentNode;
      }
      ulElement = element.parentNode.parentNode;
      aElements = ulElement.querySelectorAll("li > a");
      tabContents = document.getElementById("tabs-id").querySelectorAll(".tab-content > div");
      for(let i = 0 ; i < aElements.length; i++){
        aElements[i].classList.remove("text-white");
        aElements[i].classList.remove("bg-pink-600");
        aElements[i].classList.add("text-pink-600");
        aElements[i].classList.add("bg-white");
        tabContents[i].classList.add("hidden");
        tabContents[i].classList.remove("block");
      }
      element.classList.remove("text-pink-600");
      element.classList.remove("bg-white");
      element.classList.add("text-white");
      element.classList.add("bg-pink-600");
      document.getElementById(tabID).classList.remove("hidden");
      document.getElementById(tabID).classList.add("block");
    }
  </script>
  <%= javascript_pack_tag 'top/index' %>
